data.title: 1959 Press Photo Mary Rockefeller, wife of New York Governor Nelson Rockefeller
data.meta_description: This is an original press photo. Photo is dated 03-11-1959. It may contain wrinkles, cracks, and possibly even tears due to its age and how it was handled before it got to us. A scanner may interpret colors and contrast differently than human eyes will, so it is possible that the actual photograph may be slightly darker or lighter in person.
